{"word":"νίκη 2","slug":"νίκη 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n111343\" key=\"ni/kh2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νίκη</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπεροχή τις,</foreign> cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:1:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.178</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ AB\">AB</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">315</biblScope> </bibl>; the compd. of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φιλο-</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νεῖκος</foreign> would be <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Φιλονεικής;</foreign> the sense <sense id=\"n111343.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">contentious</tr_> arises naturally from <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fond of victory;</tr_> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">685</biblScope> </bibl> (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φιλονικία</foreign> sub fin.) we have <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φιλονικίαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12</biblScope></bibl></cit>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">36</biblScope></bibl>, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φιλονικίᾳ</foreign> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OGI\">OGI</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">335.7</biblScope> </bibl> (Pergam., decree of Pitane, <date TEIform=\"date\">ii B. C.</date>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-νῑκ-</foreign> is also found in late documents, as <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:157:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ POxy.\">POxy.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">157.1</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(vi A. D.)</date>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}